duck: Abingdon, Oxfordshire - Abingdon or archaically Abingdon-on-Thames is a market town and civil parish in Oxfordshire, England.
towns definition: a community that is dependent on one firm for all or most of the necessary services or functions of town life (as employment, housing, and stores).
